---
const { attempt = 'premium' } = Astro.props;
const deployUrl = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_DEPLOY_URL ?? 'https://deploy.easylink.hu';
---
<section id="top" class:list={["hero", attempt]}>
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">Easylink ügyvitel + AI</span>
      <h1>Cégvezetés, könnyedén.</h1>
      <p>Felejtsd el a táblázatokat! Olyan ügyviteli rendszert adunk a kezedbe, amivel egyetlen, átlátható felületen irányíthatod a számlázást, az adminisztrációt és az ügyfélnyilvántartást.</p>
      <div class="actions"><a class="button button-primary" href={deployUrl}>Demót kérek</a><a class="button button-secondary" href={deployUrl}>Próbáld ki ingyen</a></div>
    </div>
    <div class="visual" aria-hidden="true"><div class="orb"></div><div class="panel"><b>Mai üzleti pulzus</b><span>+28% gyorsabb admin</span><span>12 nyitott számla</span><span>AI javaslat: 3 prioritás</span></div></div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
.hero{overflow:hidden;background:radial-gradient(circle at 75% 20%,rgba(174,255,0,.22),transparent 28%),linear-gradient(135deg,var(--color-navy),#080a34);color:var(--color-white);padding:clamp(86px,11vw,150px) 0}.hero-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;gap:48px;align-items:center}.hero p{max-width:760px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.78);font-size:1.1rem}.actions{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap}.visual{min-height:430px;position:relative;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);background:linear-gradient(145deg,rgba(255,255,255,.14),rgba(255,255,255,.04));border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);box-shadow:var(--shadow-soft);overflow:hidden}.orb{position:absolute;inset:54px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,var(--color-neon),transparent 60%);filter:blur(8px);opacity:.75}.panel{position:absolute;left:36px;right:36px;bottom:36px;display:grid;gap:12px;padding:24px;border-radius:24px;background:rgba(15,17,89,.78);border:1px solid rgba(174,255,0,.28);backdrop-filter:blur(12px)}.panel span{padding:12px 14px;border-radius:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.08)}.futuristic .visual:before{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(174,255,0,.18) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(174,255,0,.16) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:54px 54px;mask-image:radial-gradient(circle,black,transparent 72%)}@media(max-width:860px){.hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.visual{min-height:320px}.actions{display:grid}}
</style>
